---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="ABOUT" description="The story of Kritix - from GTA on a dusty PC to chasing the solo founder dream.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative border-b-2 border-[#FAFAF8] overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background Image -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
      <img
        src="/about-bg.jpg"
        alt=""
        class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-40"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#0A0A0A] via-[#0A0A0A]/70 to-transparent"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 md:gap-16 items-center md:items-start">
        <!-- Profile Photo -->
        <div class="w-40 h-40 md:w-52 md:h-52 border-2 border-[#FAFAF8] flex-shrink-0 overflow-hidden">
          <img
            src="/kritix.jpg"
            alt="Kritix"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>

        <!-- Text -->
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold mb-4">
            I'M <span class="text-[#C45A3B]">GANESH</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-[#FAFAF8]/80 mb-4">
            but the internet knows me as <span class="text-[#C45A3B]">@itskritix</span>
          </p>
          <p class="text-[#FAFAF8]/60">
            aspiring solo founder. building my way up.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Quick Facts -->
  <section class="border-b-2 border-[#FAFAF8]">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 divide-x-0 md:divide-x-2 divide-y-2 md:divide-y-0 divide-[#FAFAF8]">
        <div class="p-6">
          <p class="text-sm opacity-60 mb-1">BASED IN</p>
          <p class="font-bold">PUNE, INDIA</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <p class="text-sm opacity-60 mb-1">STATUS</p>
          <p class="font-bold text-[#C45A3B]">BUILDING</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <p class="text-sm opacity-60 mb-1">MUSIC</p>
          <p class="font-bold">TOP 0.12% WEEKND LISTENER</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <p class="text-sm opacity-60 mb-1">DREAM</p>
          <p class="font-bold">SOLO FOUNDER</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Origin Story -->
  <section class="border-b-2 border-[#FAFAF8] py-16">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">HOW IT STARTED</h2>
      <div class="max-w-3xl space-y-6">
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          i was maybe 4 or 5 when my dad brought home a PC. 
          i didn't know what code was. i just wanted to play GTA and those 
          old 2007 retro games i can't even remember the names of anymore.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-[#FAFAF8]/80">
          when we moved to Mumbai for my dad's job, i'd go to the neighbor's 
          house just to play on their computer. games were everything.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          somewhere along the way, movies and songs showed me hackers doing 
          crazy stuff on screens. that's when i got curious about what's 
          actually happening behind the games i loved.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-[#C45A3B]">
          gaming led me to code. weird origin story, but it's mine.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Real Talk Section -->
  <section class="border-b-2 border-[#FAFAF8] py-16">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">REAL TALK</h2>
      <div class="max-w-3xl space-y-6">
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          i haven't achieved anything crazy yet. no viral product. no big exit. 
          no "10x engineer" stories. just a guy with a degree and a lot of 
          experiments that haven't blown up.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-[#FAFAF8]/80">
          but i'm working on it. every single day. 
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          i work a 9-5 as a founding engineer at Nidana. after hours, 
          i'm building <span class="text-[#C45A3B]">BrainBox</span> — my first real attempt at a SaaS. 
          zero users so far. haven't done any marketing. but the product is being built.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-[#FAFAF8]/80">
          i want to be like the people i look up to — solo founders running 
          multiple companies, living life on their own terms. 
          i'm not there. but i'm trying.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Things I Love -->
  <section class="border-b-2 border-[#FAFAF8] py-16">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">THINGS I LOVE</h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-0">
        <div class="border-2 border-[#FAFAF8] p-6 md:border-r-0">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-[#C45A3B]">CODE</h3>
          <p class="text-sm opacity-80">
            it's not just work, it's my thing. i use Claude, AI tools, 
            do experiments. coding is how i think.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-2 border-[#FAFAF8] p-6 md:border-r-0 border-t-0 md:border-t-2">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-[#C45A3B]">GAMING</h3>
          <p class="text-sm opacity-80">
            COC, League of Legends, Mobile Legends, Township, Kingsroth. 
            been gaming since before i could spell "gaming".
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-2 border-[#FAFAF8] p-6 border-t-0 md:border-t-2">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-[#C45A3B]">MUSIC</h3>
          <p class="text-sm opacity-80">
            top 0.12% listener of The Weeknd. also Ariana Grande. 
            i listen to everything — different genres, different languages.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Future Dreams -->
  <section class="py-16 border-b-2 border-[#FAFAF8]">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">SOMEDAY...</h2>
      <div class="max-w-3xl space-y-4">
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-[#C45A3B]">></span>
          <span>travel solo. see the whole world.</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-[#C45A3B]">></span>
          <span>run my own company. maybe multiple.</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-[#C45A3B]">></span>
          <span>live life on my terms. not a 9-5 forever.</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-[#C45A3B]">></span>
          <span>build something people actually use.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg mt-8 text-[#FAFAF8]/60">
        not there yet. but watch this space.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- GitHub Activity -->
  <section class="py-16 border-b-2 border-[#FAFAF8]" id="activity">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">GITHUB ACTIVITY</h2>

      <!-- Contribution Graph -->
      <div class="border-2 border-[#FAFAF8] p-6 overflow-x-auto">
        <img
          src="https://ghchart.rshah.org/C45A3B/itskritix"
          alt="GitHub Contribution Graph"
          class="w-full max-w-4xl"
        />
      </div>

      <a href="https://github.com/itskritix" target="_blank" class="inline-block mt-6 text-sm opacity-60 hover:opacity-100 hover:text-[#C45A3B] transition-colors">
        VIEW FULL PROFILE ->
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Connect -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">SAY HI</h2>
      <p class="opacity-80 mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        i'm always down to chat about code, startups, games, or just life.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="https://x.com/itskritix" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-brutal">
          TWITTER
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/itskritix" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-brutal">
          GITHUB
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-brutal bg-[#C45A3B] border-[#C45A3B] hover:bg-transparent hover:text-[#C45A3B]">
          CONTACT
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
